<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1940-08-03T02:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1940-08-03T02:00:00-05:00" n="439" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d439">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">711.94/1622: Telegram</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Grew</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                    State</gloss></hi></head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-08-03T16:00:00+09:00">August 3, 1940—4
                                        p.m.</date><lb/>[Received August 3—7:36 a.m.]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>660. Department’s 286, July 31, noon.<note n="36" xml:id="d439fn36"><ref target="frus1931-41v02#pg_108"><hi rend="italic">Ibid.</hi>, p. 108</ref>.</note> The sense of the
                                President’s informal comments on Mr. Matsuoka’s private message<note n="37" xml:id="d439fn37">See telegram No. 620, July 26, 6 p.m.,
                                    from the Ambassador in Japan, <ref target="frus1931-41v02#pg_105"><hi rend="italic">ibid.</hi>,
                                        p. 105</ref>.</note> was communicated informally to him
                                today by me. Mr. Matsuoka listened with interest and asked me to
                                express to the President his full appreciation <pb facs="0420" n="412" xml:id="pg_412"/> of the President’s kindness and the
                                trouble he had taken in commenting on the message.</p>
                            <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi></signed></closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>